latestPosts.caption:
Ad. Last night we had the pleasure of dining at @bettys 🍷

We adore Betty’s and to have evening dining back in Harrogate is such a delight! Their tea rooms are iconic, steeped in history and 1920s elegance and charm - this really is such a gorgeous experience. 

The new sharing plates are a welcome addition to their menu of signature dishes and famous deserts - there is something for everyone! The service is always impeccable (a special thank you to our lovely waitress Freya) and the added touch of the very talented pianist playing classical covers of contemporary music was just a joy. 

Thank you for having us Betty’s, we will be back 🤎

**Evening dining is available at @bettys Harrogate and York, Thursdays, Fridays and Saturdays from 6pm.
